node.text:
One of the most beautiful Humans to ever visit this Glorious Planet that we have mercilessly destroyed almost to all its extent. A Buddha in all of his Glory, the pinnacle of Awareness and Intelligence.
To change this, first put your House in order. Only then, will the Planet be enjoyable once more.
#JidduKrishnamurti #JidduKrishnamurtiBJWT 
#503 @jkcentre

node.text:
Pay attention Lovely people, because you are watching the Magic of a modern Buddha. But not only a Buddha, a Master. So logical, so articulated, that even Gautam The Buddha would rejoice in such poetry that comes out of Jiddu Krishnamurti’s mouth. If you didn’t learn anything from a Buddha throughout your life, you have wasted your life. So I implore you, pay attention to whatsoever a Buddha has to say, because he or she is going to raise your awareness exponentially.
Nothing is the same after an encounter with a Buddha. Nothing. You might not know what brought you to him, you might think that you are close to him for an entirely different reason than the real one. And the real one is that you didn’t stand a chance, he called you and you came, because that’s how it works. Your entire being had been craving for Truth and when the Master made himself available, you came to drink from him, to rejoice in him, to absorb all that he has to give you, and trust me, he has the whole Universe to offer to you, you just have to drop yourself and let your guard down. Then, Existence will swallow you and you will realize Eternity this very moment.
Look how beautiful Jiddu was. I would had hugged him, kissed his feet, the he would had kissed mine, and after this protocolary nonsense, we would had laughed and stayed in silence looking at our kids in shock. You want to hear the punchline? Neither Krishnamurti, neither Papa Bear and neither anyone or anything else, exist.
This is the joke of jokes. Only a Buddha will understand these words. YET I AM HERE...
AES DHAMMO SANANTANO.
#Krishnamurti #KrishnamurtiBJWT
#PapaBearChronicles 
@jkcentre

node.text:
If Papa Bear talks the talk, it is because he walks the walk. He might look small in the vid, but he’s way bigger than a Rottweiler, and obviously, his bite had the strength of a Lion’s bite that size, with full fangs as you will see on the second vid if you scroll. But I trusted my Son and everything went great. Now, him and my daughter Angel, his girlfriend, are running happily next to Karma and Ali. By the way, you can see Alicito and Afriquita all the way behind us :)
#SimbiAndAngelForever #SaveLions

node.text:
It is with a bittersweet feeling that I have to tell you that Simbi died yesterday of natural causes. I had already given the instruction one day before of putting him to sleep because he was not doing well, and obviously, since Angel was in a worst physical form than Simbi, it was necessary to put her to sleep also. Vanessa was there to say good bye, but when she arrived, Simbi had already left on his own. There’s no way that I would had left a sick, widowed and genetically impaired Lioness all by herself since I can’t put her with any other female or male or they would had killed her automatically. When Vanessa arrived, Angelita was by Simbi’s side flanking him. These two “Dwarves” are a product of inbreeding in Mexico. I rescued Angel from a University where they kept her as a pet around 6 years ago and I can’t remember where Simbi came from, but they were the perfect match for each other until their bodies gave up. Angel was overall in a worst shape but women are more resilient. She almost never moved from that position with her belly up and Simbi had two seizures last week and stopped moving two days ago. But it made me super happy to find out that he left on his own at his own time, that was my boy, a Warrior, regardless of his body. Angelita was pure Heart and was Simbi’s faithful companion till the end. Simbi would not stop moving his feet in happiness every time that he saw me, he was super excited every time so I trusted him and entered with him two times. He might be small but his jaw was the jaw of a Lion, but that’s how much I trusted him. It was an absolute Honor to care for these Angels for 5 years or more. They lived and died with Dignity at OUR SANCTUARY…
#SimbiAndAngelForever #SaveLions

node.text:
Do you understand why I can’t stand human crybabies? Nothing worse than a poorly educated kid. My huge kids were educated with Pure Love and the annoying finger (Plus their Dad’s megaphone voice). Never hit them, never punished them except with my absence. If they behaved well, they had everything. If they misbehaved, they had everything except their Dad’s presence and the felt terrible for acting out with me. That is my method of education. As simple as this…
#AlisPrideBJWT #PapaBearChronicles
